  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if there is a correlation between tumor response
      after 3 doses of chemotherapy by induction using Docetaxel, Cisplatine and 5-Fluorouracile
      for advanced stage epidermoid carcinomas of the upper aero digestive tract and the presence
      of one or a combination of 3 genetic polymorphisms and/or 5 intra-tumoral transcriptional
      modifications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
